content: standujar: Focused on enhancing the Solana plugin by fixing a lazy loading issue in `SolanaWalletService` via PR elizaos-plugins/plugin-solana#18 and bumping its version, while also initiating a new feature to implement a unified messaging API in elizaos/eliza#6095. Their code changes reflect a balanced effort across feature work, bug fixes, and other tasks, primarily touching code and tests.
